APPLICATION README:

This application is designed to provide a simple management capability for a (Competitive) Soccer Team or Club.

Acknowledgements:
1. How to integrate Active Admin with Devise into a single User Model
REFERENCE : http://dan.doezema.com/2012/02/how-to-implement-a-single-user-model-with-rails-activeadmin-and-devise/

Issues:
1. Differences between local environment and Production on Time zones - creates complications when creating Game Slots
across PDT and PST boundaries. The code in 'lib/tasks/setup_club.rake' should be refactored to handle this environment
